# Richena Papeterie Web

Monorepo:

- apps/web  -> Next.js (site)
- apps/cms  -> Sanity Studio (conteúdo)
- infra     -> VPS/Traefik deployment
- docs      -> documentação

## Dev (local)
- Web: cd apps/web -> 
pm run dev
- CMS: cd apps/cms -> 
pm run dev
